///macros_colourcodes();
/*

	These are [Colour Code]s stored as [integer]s 
	While registered as hex, GMS will convert and store these as integers at 
	project build, so the value you see here isn't exactly what you get in game
	
	$bbggrr		GMS Format			
	#rrbbgg		Standard Format (Photoshop etc)
		(rr = red as hex, bb = blue as hex, gg = green as hex)
		
	[WIP] Add tools for easy colour creation
	
*/

